Version 0.4.0 (2017-12-26)
--------------------------
- renamed organization and packages from com.bfil to io.bfil
- published the library to Bintray
- updated akka-actor to 2.3.16 and 2.5.8


Version 0.3.0 (2015-01-14)
--------------------------
- added Scala 2.12 support
- updated to Akka 2.4 for Scala 2.12 and Scala 2.12 releases


Version 0.2.0 (2015-03-22)
--------------------------
- removed dependency on shapeless
- simplified the creation of custom chainable actions
- split the testkit into a separate module
- testkit simplification


Version 0.1.0 (2014-06-23)
--------------------------
first public release
